{"text": "Call of Duty 2 is a classic FPS. Set during WWII with a lengthy campaign filled with action, you will play through different factions (Russia, Britain and US) with authentic weaponry to use throughout. You can pickup enemy weapons, man mounted machine guns and there is a level you will control a tank. The level design is very well done and you will fight through a wide variety of levels. COD2 was amazing when it first came out and still holds up incredibly well today. Well worth playing through, I highly recommend it. Very refreshing to play through a great single player campaign when the majority of shooters today focus on the multiplayer.", "appid": "2630", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970897684", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569585600.0}
