{"text": "This game where you play as a goat to try to cause as much chaos and wreak havoc among the innocent victims is one that i enjoyed a lot. It is a simple game to run in terms of hardware. It is great to play with friends and work together in co-op or vs missions which is up to you to decide! The flexibility of this sandbox game allows for a variety of different audiences to enjoy. The game doesn't have challenging mechanics which makes it easy to pick up. The game allows for people to do whatever they please without real-life consequence which appeals to a large majority of people. It is easy to invite a buddy to play and sink many hours into this game, however, if you are playing this unfortunately, unpopular game in todays day and age, it will get very bland,stale and boring very quickly meaning the enjoyed hours you put into this game will be limited. If anyone wants a more family friendly sandbox game with simple controls, this game is for you. There are many trophies and characters which can be collected. This can be a reward system or a way for you to have a clear target in terms of the goals you want to complete. There are also many easter eggs which are really fun to find. The achievements of the game are fairly simple and can be finished quickly if that is what you are aiming to do.", "appid": "265930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198265846991", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584532800.0}
