{"text": "It's a very cool driving game with that fantastic 80's retro/Tron look. You collect points by driving around on a procedural generated track. This means everytime you drive, the track changes. However there will be portion you'll get familiar with eventually The more your drift, the more points you are able to achieve in a less ammount of time. The game contains a lot of fitting retro music which you'll love!  There is a leaderboard which contains the high scores, the scores of the ones next fo to you, and another to compare to with your friends. The achievements are relatively easy to obtain, although the drifting ones might take a bit more effort to get.  There are car other purchases you can make after you get enough money.  You can also alter the cars look and tamper with them a little bit.", "appid": "881130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013321249", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1593518400.0}
