{"text": "Ultra Space Battle Brawl is a way too good arcade title based in part conceptually on Pong, wrapped in a pronounced Street Fighter vibe where players swing bats to make contact with the ball to attack your opponents targets.  Destroying all targets or leading when time expires ....  WINNER!!!! ....  or else .... LOSER!!!! .... Single player story mode against multiple character personalities with continues if you are a .... LOSER!!!! ....  Two difficultly levels normal and ultra.  Normal challenge is easy though the last character personality is difficult on normal.  Each player builds a power-up bar until full which enables a character's special attack. Versus mode Split Screen PVP and Split Screen COOP make an awesome local party game.  Supports remote play though I gather the parties would require an immaculate connection since game-play is fast, furious and frenetic. Highly recommended.", "appid": "658500", "steamid": "profiles/76561197979445690", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601467200.0}
