{"text": "This is a rather unusual Tower Defense project with an interesting story, humor and the ability to raise the level of your character. The main advantages are: extraordinary gameplay - I have never played towers in a cooperative before, simultaneously attack and defend, change the enemy's movement,blocking the way for him by detachments. An excellent pitch, a variety of everything: locations, types of enemies and created units. Opportunities to go through the same location in different ways - a lot. The game really makes you move your brains, choosing the optimal plan for arranging troops and used magic to get the desired goal or bonuses for a special passing of the level. Changing the complexity of the same cards significantly changes the tactics of the game, but is also encouraged by resources to improve its player and city. Sound and visual design is also at altitude. Pleasant music immerses in the fantasy world, and gradually grows during the battle. Really fascinating gameplay, the game will not let you get bored. Of the minuses only one, this is a small online in the game. Cooperative missions are not obligatory, the single game is also very interesting, but when I found a comrade in the cooperative, the game process changed significantly, now it was necessary to think together, and it was really exciting. The original gameplay, the ability to build a city, fun dialogs and quests, level up skills of the player and units, playing along with random people / friends and against them, achievements and much more, the game definitely worth buying. 10 old wizards out of 10 (Old wizard said that I'm smart)", "appid": "562500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198193183377", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509105600.0}
