{"text": "I have about 400 hours and still have fun. I love the gunfights and the movement of this game.  The raiding  system is fantastic but there should be more materials to build with, to defend your base better. My biggest problem is that the game does have a map problem. All maps are kinda the same like germany, russia and france. I think that the map elver is a step in the right direction because its something new. Maybe a map with many small islands on it would be cool or a map where you need to go in 1 direction and just have 1 spawn for everyone so its harder to get the good loot. I do love this game but it has not enough content for progress making players, like guns, ressorces, build options/build materials (like stronger walls). Ps This game is anwesome and for the most players there is enough content, but for me as a experienced player, it should be more Challenging.", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198377964855", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580558400.0}
