{"text": "Hmm, touchy. Being a â™¥â™¥â™¥ is one of those rare games which genuinely taught us two main things, that every youngsters are ravaged and confused with. One is lust where everybody just goes into hookup for temporary pleasure with no  string attachments thus getting this done without any regrets while the other side shows the divine spirit of love where one should experience at least once in their lifetime, keeping short term pleasures aside. Which side you enjoyed the most, shall decide your ongoing gameplay. It has also taught that always being a stud +â™¥â™¥â™¥ does not get you always what you wish for, it may look cool but it has own set of regrets which is understandable for not unlocking the scenes. Sometimes you just need to blend with ''Chickks\", without taking things personal to get what you have wished for, aiming for correct choices. You cannot take every situation in your hands, you are bound to sacrifice few and expect for the best. This is how university students feel (even now i have felt), these kinda days truly should be experienced with all salts and melodic dramas, twisting plots, fantasies coming true, learning lessons of life, worth keeping all as a memory. Bully or being bullied, winner all loser, ugly or beautiful, dumb or smart everybody has got their part, this game has truly shown it all. These all touched my heart, sometimes made me emotional, sometimes made me fell proud.  And the best part of it, finally accept who you are, be grateful to the decisions you made. Now on a serious note, Hey PINK CAKE, if you are READING THIS, if the season 2 is now fully developed, just release it already. I AM GONNA PAY TRIPLE(3X) THE PRICE of the original price for REAL. - MightyGaayLord", "appid": "1126320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198325876315", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594382400.0}
