{"text": "Cool classic fighting game with epic fights and cool charismatic characters.The music here is just wow.It is best to play in stereo headphones for a complete immersion in the atmosphere of the game.A very cool combat system, each character needs his own approach and his own tactics especially in the performance of combo attacks.There are quite a lot of them and it will be quite difficult to remember them all.The game has a network mode, it is a lot of fun playing with a friend and laugh at laugh at mistake and failure together, there are even very funny moments.To play online with other players, you need to train a lot of your skills in management and tactics since there are masters of gamepads and just geniuses who will sit on the mountain in the temple and will be watch at you doubtfully.And in order to prove your strength you need to train and learn from other players.Of the most interesting characters in my opinion, it is worth noting Kyo Kusanagi, as well as Goro Daimon, Mai Shiranui, Yuri Sakazaki, Billy Kane and Ryo Sakazaki.The game is cool and worth attention. Thank you! (Sorry for my english)", "appid": "222940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198326115981", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "19", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1583064000.0}
