{"text": "Wizard 101 is a blast-from-the-past rpg fantasy game within a mixture of a card/spell casting mechanic that provides the player with a setting of the heavy grind ahead that is the wizarding world. The extended story quests, which have been continued over the many years of it being released, mean that the player can come back every now and then to continue their wizard legacy. Overall, the game runs well enough for the standard computer, however, the lack of freedom in this game can be an issue for new and existing players, aswell as the repetition of continously running back and fourth doing quests after mission after journey. But of course, the game comes back with witty story and a large cast of characters, items and unique ideology of how the user wishes to play the game, which in saying, lets the game continue to be enjoyable and a ball of fun, especially with friends. Wizard101 is an iconic game that has stuck around for many years and still has an active community to this day, and has done well in thanking them with content and nostalga.' Wizard101 - 7.5/10 - Rom", "appid": "799960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068084558", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0}
