{"text": "Hotline Miami is a brutally entertaining top down shooter, that has a psychadelic retro atmosphere and surreal storyline.  Even though its a pixel graphics game, it is very pretty to look at with bright neon colors and a stylish art design.  The game is extremely fast paced, addrenaline packed, and full of blood and violence.  This game is not for the feint of heart.  There are more ways to kill someone than you can count, and the death animations and gore are well done.  The gameplay is very challenging and will test you reaction skills, one mistake and your dead. There are alot of gruesome weapons and styles of play to tackle each unique level. The story is trippy and intentionally hard to follow which adds to the dark mystery of the game.   The soundtrack is amazing and sets the tone and pace of the game.  This game is on the shorter side but its challneging nature and brutal combat will keep you coming back for more.  Hotline Miami is a great game that if given the chance will surely blow you away.", "appid": "219150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080118624", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518004800.0}
