{"text": "Pro: The music is awesome.  Has a nice retro look. Con: The game is insanely hard and lacks a lot of context.  It's not clear as to what will and won't damage you.  Sometimes a laser attack goes through and damages me, and then there are other times where it does nothing.  Sometimes the hornets damage me, sometimes they don't.  It's also not clear what even restores health as I sometimes get some health restored only for it to be taken away fast by an undodgeable attack. Overall: I suppose you can give it a try, but expect a lot of frustration.", "appid": "1311640", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977724919", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596024000.0}
