{"text": "Unbearably boring and obtuse. I went through every room and exhausted every option and all I got was a redundant elevator, a piece of paper, and a doll I can't put down that I'm supposed to \"warm up\". I opened every window, flipped every switch, opened every cabinet, touched every touchable object, went everywhere the game would let me and could make no more progress. I played for 31 minutes at 3x speed because the walking speed is unbearably slow. That equates to 90 minutes of playtime. And absolutely nothing happened except a couple flashbacks. I saw a keyring, but the game wouldn't let me pick it up.  I lost interest and refunded it. GG.", "appid": "433100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198261957551", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597233600.0}
{"text": "Even though i support this type of trash cinema, Kung Fury wasnt really that good. Trash cinema is an art , not just some b00lsh3it put up in 1 day. A good example of a good movie in the same genre is the Iron Sky, which is way way better than this.  Some jokes and puns in Kung Fury are actually funny, and so are some of the scenes, but for the most part this really was a trashy movie. The raving positive reviews for this movie are only due to the fact that this movie was purposely made too look like trash and all 14 year olds and the sheeple eat it up thinking that somehow it's a form of art, but in reality there is very little substance in this movie. If you read the reviews, youll see that most of them are just mindless one liners, quotes from the movie with no real purpose, and just pure nonesense.  All of which are supposedly funny. \"WOW THIS MOVIE TRIED TO BE SO BAD< ITS ACTUALLY GOOD!' lAZOR RAPTORS MADE IT FOR ME' - no, not really, this movie really is just trash, and laser raptors were in the movie for only 10 seconds, eeDeeot. But if you like mindless stuff with no substance promoted as art then go ahead and jump on the bandwagon with the rest of monkeys. If you consider yourself to have some sort of intelligence, you probably wouldnt like this trash. if youre one with the crowd, then this trash is for you. 5/10", "appid": "374570", "steamid": "profiles/76561197962405690", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479038400.0}
