{"text": "Despite reading the negative reviews for this game I decided to buy it. After buying the game I launched it, which brought me to the frontier launcher where I had to create an account, I was a bit annoyed but whatever. So I make my account and when I try to log in through the launcher it tells me that the server was unable to process my request. I assumed the servers might have been down, but after a quick search I realized that the servers were in fine condition. I tried going on their support page to find out how to fix the issue, but the page was really not customer friendly, and I couldn't find what I was looking for. I completely reinstalled the game only for the same error to occur. The only thing I can get this game to do is run the demo FOR A GAME I ALREADY PAID FOR. I'm just going to refund this game if I don't get a response that will help me.", "appid": "359320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198353343528", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555588800.0}
