{"text": "I have started the game and can already see some issues out of the gate.  However, lets start with some positives first. Positives: - - - Now that we've got those out of the way, let continue to the negatives.  Negatives: -The \"player model\" is all around â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ and looks like that one scene from harry potter when he lost his bones. -It seems like the dev team forgot to add options for controller location because for some reason the game thinks my controller is a yard away from where my hand is. On top of that my in-game hand is rotated and twisted to be not even close to where my real hand is.  (Issue with the game not SteamVR) -Gun models look fine except with the fact that they have a completely different design pattern then the rest of the game. Your sausage fingers don't even FIT inside the trigger guard and rely on clipping to make it look natural. Hell, on the AK, your finger doesn't even touch the trigger when you fire. -I was unable to grab a gun with both hands, I can see that you can in the trailer but I can't within game. Maybe it was the gun I was using but who the â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ holds an AK with one hand. -You grab Magazines out of your â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥, not a pouch. -The \"mobility\" it offers feels artificial and has zero (caliber VR) weight. -when a grab something, I can't use my index finger. I have to grab something with 3 fingers or else i drop it. How on earth does that make any sense? -Doesn't even offer a conversion to freedom units. How the hell am i supposed to know how far or high something is in CM or whatever. The height calibration doesn't do â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ to help with the player model either. -This game has been out for 2 YEARS and most of these problems are easy to fix. They are charging $25 for this game STILL. -The screenshots look nothing like the heaping pile of garbage I just \"played\". Call of Duty and battlefield are better than this. Please FIX this game. I would offer to PAY you to fix it, but I already have. This game has potential, however it is being wasted on â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ mechanics and poor designs. I'm going to go play H3VR and buy Pavlov instead.", "appid": "877200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198144462058", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1605528000.0}
