{"text": "The Multiplayer Mode in Resident Evil Franchise is not your part Capcom. You did a great job back in the days with RE5 to implement an addiciting game mode like Mercenaries/Reunion.  But this Resistance mode is pure crap you going to jump on a trend like Dead by Daylight or whatever. I really dislike the mechanics in this multiplayer mode. Also why I have to play random young teenage kids. You making the zombies looking bad, when teenage kids can handle zombies, lickers, tyrants or whatever...  This game took away time to create Resident Evil 3 remake. I donÂ´t get it why you gonna investigate ressources for this game mode.  RE3 lack of it. ItÂ´s like you felt guilty and put this combination together to get a decent argument for forcing people to investigate 60 â‚¬. The price is not worth it, because of this resistance game!", "appid": "952070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086717619", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586347200.0}
