{"text": "Trailers were misleading... This is a very bad copy-paste of L4D with no Walking Dead stories whatsoever. Overkill's \"Horde Mode\" should be the title, fight ten trizilion zombies while patching gates and defenses that will hold up for...hmmm 30 seconds (which makes you wonder why the hell you need these in 1st place) 4 boring characters only, no soul, no real goals, and none of The Walking Dead vibe behind this game whatsoever. I was in the beta, then 3 stages into main game, and it is the same. Bashing zombies.... I did that in L4D and it was fun, did that in Dead Island and it was fun, did it in State of Decay and it was fun... But here?.... Nope. It is blend, bad, very bad to ultra bad. No i am not 12 years old, im a grown man, playing games since forever. Yes i love Overkill, and zombie games as well. No i will not play this though, especially for that insane price.... This should have been a $30.00 game seriously.", "appid": "717690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038340267", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541505600.0}
