{"text": "Garfield Kart is by far the best game I have played to date. There is deep lore and an amazing tale to be told in Garfield and Jon's adventures of karting, and the recent inclusion of Nermal as a player has provided me with even more hours of enjoyment. This game has shaped my life and made me a better person in general.  While some people claim this is a \"rip off of Super Mario Kart,\" most don't realize that Garfield has roots going back to 183 BC while Mario Kart merely debuted in 1992. Furthermore, the graphics featured in this game are incredible and it even includes the latest breakthrough in technology, \"ray tracing\" which is definitely a pro from me.  The downside of the graphics, however, is that this means the game requires roughly 4 Titan V's or better, though at the small cost of ~$15,000 worth of hardware, the gaming experience received from Garfield Kart is without a doubt worth it. Strongly recommend, 10/10", "appid": "903730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069149241", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "14", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1559390400.0}
