{"text": "Fun game, if not as deep as one would imagine going into it. The environment has very little variety. Before I started, it looked like it had a plethora of options, but this is essentially a \"build base\", \"raid base\", \"gather resources\" game, with a whole bunch of camping added in. It's fun with friends, but the community in general is toxic, as you tend to find with these types of games. Fun for a while, but I can't recommend for long-term play.", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561197989306029", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587816000.0}
