{"text": "First off, the excuse that this is early acess is no longer valid, having been used so many times that the phrase is meaningless. The community is so ****in toxic that you can't even voice your opinion about the game (if it's negative mind you, they love positivity). The playerbase is split between those who want a game mode that was cruelly taken from them by Dondi so they can get \"feedback\", and those who worship Dondi like a ****in god, kissing the very ground he walks on, and always saying \"gr8 work Dondi\" or \"i luv you dondi, your game is perfect and nothing is wrong\". They raid servers that don't play the game how they want it, and make a mess of everything, ruining a fun time for everyone, save those who raided in the first place. Second, the devs. I have never seen a more unprofessional, tempermental, and spiteful developer in all of my life. His attitude is terrible, scorning those who want help in playing the game, stating that they are \"too weak to survive\" or, \"they are bad hunters\". The ***k is your problem mate, you obviously have never beem subject to criticism or hateful comments, or you would have been handling them better.  You are so sensitive that mere comments set you off, going on a spiel saying that you don't take crap from nobody, and that no one's suggestions matter, and that your vision for the game is perfect. And lastly, for those fooled by the trailers and videos posted by big time Youtubers, thinking that this is a good investment for your money, don't buy it. It's a waste of time to play, currently, and offers no reward for investing your money and time into this half ***ed attempt at a simulator. Ciao", "appid": "376210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198067319230", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "76", "votes_funny": "9", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1469534400.0}
