{"text": "TL;DR: Don't buy or Play this game til the developers fix their crap. Now personally, I enjoy this game alot. I find it a really fun to play MMO. Only one problem, And no. It's not P2W, It's not crappy controls, It's not the gold spammers in the chat... It's the Developers themselves.  Now, Here's why. First of all... To use World chat or Channel chat you must pay IRL money... 30 Merits for World chat ($0.30) per message. or like 3 Merits for Channel. That's pretty bad right? Now get this... Max level is 50, You can hit that in less than a day pretty easy if your doing your quests, However! The only thing to look forward to is the dungeons, And raids, And their some of the best content in the game, except for a major flaw... You get to do 10 per day (You stop getting rewarded items if you do anymore) and a cap of 30 per week! That means that 4 out of the 7 days of the week you can't do any more dungeons on your character unless you take the time out of your day to grind ANOTHER character to 50 just to get 10 more dungeon runs per day... It's bad. REALLY BAD. And worst offender of all, One of the developers has actively said that they are adding in another type of raids with \"Less\" caps on them for people to do in the meantime for the other 4 days... Nothing about \"Yeah, These caps are temporary or bad and we plan on removing them on full release\" This is a INTENDED FEATURE... This reason alone ruins the game for any hardcore gamers or casual gamers alike! And for this very reason... I say avoid this game like the plague... Avoid it as if it was a uncurable plague that the moment you come into contact with it you die! At least til this gets handled. If it was fixed, I'd say yeah, The game is amazing! 4/5. But since it's not, and the end game is basically locked after 10 dungeons. The game don't even belong on the list!", "appid": "560380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018240066", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "495", "votes_funny": "67", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539000000.0}
